<h3>
<ol>
  <li>Become inspired by mediocre productions.</li>
<li>Don’t covert production and experimentation recipe.</li>
<li>Always leave the edges rough, so that someone can cut themselves.</li>
<li>A photoshop’d joke is deep and meaningful.</li>
<li>Take the knife to cultural icons and produce: produce the produce for the recipe and destroy the recipe.</li>
<li>Follow and muddy up every else’s recipe; pun and play, annihilate and resurrect meaning.</li></ol>
<em>Peter Nowogrodzki</em>
